GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 6h June, 2003
15 Jyaistha , 1925(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 5h June,
2003 Shri Satyabrata Mookerjee, Minister of State in the Ministry of Planning,
Minister of State in the Ministry of Statistics and Programme Implementation and
Minister of State in the Department of Atomic Energy and Department of Space
assumed the additional charge of the office of Minister of State in the Ministry of
Commerce and Industry.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of the
Planning Commission.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
